I. INTRODUCTION
script allows to format blast databases, set galaxy reference format and to create galaxy reference megablast loc files

II. DOCUMENTATION
Usage:

$ set_galaxy_blastdb.sh -help
$ set_galaxy_blastdb.sh -fasta filename -p T|F -n blastdb_name -fastadesc ncbi-gk|other

where :

-fasta filename
-p T ; if your database are protein sequences
-p F ; if your database are nucleotide sequences
-n blastdb_name ; set database filename for Galaxy Loc File
-fastadesc ncbi-gk ; option if your fasta ID is like gi|gi-number|gb|accesión|locus
-fastadesc other ; your own sequence IDs

to run :
$ ./set_galaxy_blastdb.sh -fasta /media/xlinux/genomes/galaxy/palomero/megablast/genome.fasta -p F -n my-genomedb-name -fastadesc ncbi-gk

